Nigerian singer, Timaya has congratulated American star, Rihanna on her pregnancy.
The expectant mom proudly flaunted her baby bump in New York City.
Rihanna and A$AP Rocky are going to be parents soon as they are already expecting their first kid.

As millions of fans across the world congratulate the couple, the cold outside corner joined in the pageantry.
Timaya took to his social media to share a 7-year-old photo he took with Rihanna during a visit to her home country, Barbados.
He penned down a sweet caotion and reminisced on the moments he shared with her in the photo.

Congrats @rihanna , keep shining like the Diamond that you’ve always been. Papichulo wrote
See his tweet:

Congrats @rihanna , keep shining like the Diamond that you’ve always been  pic.twitter.com/uks0xwvX7f
